00157 static void print_list_ident( FILE * output, list_items * list, unsigned int indent ){
00158     
00159     generic_item * curr_item;
00160     
00161     /* sanity check */
00162     if (!list) return;
00163     
00164     curr_item=(*list);
00165     
00166     while (curr_item)
00167     {
00168         
00169         if ( curr_item->type == TYPE_BLOCK )
00170         {
00171             fprintf(output,"%*s<BLOCK '%s'>\n",indent, " ",curr_item->item.block.block_name);
00172             print_list_ident( output, &curr_item->item.block.block_content, indent+3 );
00173             fprintf(output,"%*s</BLOCK '%s'>\n",indent, " ",curr_item->item.block.block_name);
00174         }
00175         else
00176         {
00177             /* affectation */
00178             fprintf(output,"%*sKEY: '%s', VALUE: '%s'\n",indent, " ",curr_item->item.affect.varname, curr_item->item.affect.varvalue );
00179         }
00180         
00181         curr_item=curr_item->next;
00182     }
00183         
00184 }

00198 static void free_list_items_recurse(list_items * list)
00199 {
00200     generic_item * curr_item;
00201     generic_item * next_item;
00202     
00203     /* sanity check */
00204     if (!list) return;
00205     
00206     curr_item=(*list);
00207     
00208     while (curr_item)
00209     {
00210       
00211       next_item = curr_item->next;
00212       
00213       if ( curr_item->type == TYPE_BLOCK )
00214       {
00215           free_list_items_recurse( &curr_item->item.block.block_content );
00216       }
00217       
00218       free( curr_item );
00219       curr_item = next_item;
00220         
00221     }    
00222     return ;    
00223 }

00229 void config_free_list(list_items * list){
